.sp
Besides, by using zstyle command, you can change default value:
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
$ zstyle ":zplug:tag" hook\-build "echo build"
.fi
.if n \{\
.RE
.\}
.SH "EXAMPLES"
.sp
Grant a right to execute:
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
$ zplug "b4b4r07/79ee61f7c140c63d2786" \e
    as:command, \e
    from:gist, \e
    hook\-build:"chmod 755 my_script\&.sh"
.fi
